<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM11.1.5">
<l>aṅkō rāḷari yāya vuṇaṉaip</l>
<l>paṅka māviru kūṟu ceytavaṉ</l>
<l>maṅkul māmati vāṅka vēkolō</l>
<l>poṅku mākaṭal pulampu kiṉṟatē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Is it since he, who as a man-lion once rendered the demon</l>
<l>Into two pieces, so that he was defeated,</l>
<l>Snatched the great moon in the night,</l>
<l>That the roiling great sea is roaring?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
